HEADWORD: Teratoid
<hw>Ter"a*toid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/, <?/,
monster + <ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <def>Resembling a monster; abnormal;
of a pathological growth, exceedingly complex or highly organized.</def>
